1
00:00:54,680 --> 00:00:55,880
Something happened.

2
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,520
What the hell is this?

3
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,970
Wasn't this guy blacklisted ages ago?

4
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,440
A band led by someone like him

5
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:12,170
definitely won't make the cut.

6
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,840
I just started liking

7
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,000
the Wildfire Club.

8
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,440
Is it over already?

9
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:26,960
Look at this.

10
00:01:27,080 --> 00:01:28,640
The internet is going crazy.

11
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,560
He didn't plagiarize.

12
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,400
I don't care.

13
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,039
I absolutely won't accept

14
00:01:32,039 --> 00:01:33,440
a tainted singer here.

15
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:53,130
Cancel the upcoming shows for now.

16
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,840
I didn't plagiarize.

17
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,520
Liu Ma.

18
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:05,080
This is obviously pure fabrication.

19
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:05,760
I believe you.

20
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,240
So do I.

21
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,560
I stand by my brother unconditionally.

22
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:21,640
Brother.

23
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,200
Have you ever thought about it?

24
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,200
Let's take this chance

25
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:26,400
to go on stage together.

26
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,640
Show your true strength

27
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:28,970
and clear up the rumors.

28
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:33,680
Rumors aren't that easy to clear up.

29
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,480
I'm quitting the band.

30
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,400
Why?

31
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,120
Because we don't stand a chance.

32
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:46,660
Let alone clearing up any rumors.

33
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:48,520
Are you afraid your bad press

34
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,300
will affect our performance?

35
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,370
If we win the championship,

36
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,720
we can shut up all the doubters.

37
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,860
Championship.

38
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,720
Didn't I tell you?

39
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,680
This is all a setup by capital.

40
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,200
Why do you think this happened

41
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,600
right before the finals?

42
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,360
The ones who actually win

43
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,960
have already signed contracts and have scripts.

44
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:09,040
It has nothing to do with us.

45
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:09,840
Liu Ma,

46
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:12,040
are you going to keep running away from your problems?

47
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:13,570
What am I running away from?

48
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,640
I really regret it now.

49
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,600
I regret getting drunk that day

50
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:19,460
and buying you guys instruments.

51
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:21,420
I came to Lincang this time

52
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:25,960
just for the money,

53
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:28,010
not to chase music dreams with you.

54
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:42,380
Let the two of them talk alone.

55
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,370
Do you remember?

56
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,240
The first time we met,

57
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:04,960
I brought you here.

58
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:06,760
Hard to forget.

59
00:04:07,880 --> 00:04:09,610
I was scared to death back then.

60
00:04:10,320 --> 00:04:11,360
Looking at it now,

61
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,450
it feels quite healing.

62
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,730
Wildfire Club is only complete

63
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,680
with you here.

64
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,520
Actually,

65
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,460
I snuck out to see your show back then.

66
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,800
Do you respect music?

67
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,360
It's all rigged!

68
00:05:22,080 --> 00:05:23,120
Rigged!

69
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,560
So this is rock and roll.

70
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,240
It's so cool.

71
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,320
It's all rigged!

72
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,400
Let go of me!

73
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,880
Rigged! Liu Ma!

74
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,780
I've kept it with me all this time.

75
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,220
Then do you know

76
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,500
why I smashed my guitar back then?

77
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,600
I just passed the judges' office

78
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:22,560
and heard the organizer of this competition

79
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:24,560
is the boss of Sweetheart Baby Band.

80
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:27,170
They've rigged the win.

81
00:06:29,840 --> 00:06:30,800
Are you sure?

82
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:32,600
I even saw them preparing

83
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,930
the champion's banner.

84
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,400
Plus,

85
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,000
the boss has already decided.

86
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:39,770
If you go on stage today,

87
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,120
you'll just be the runner-up.

88
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:41,960
Why?

89
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:46,040
Runner-up without even competing?

90
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:46,920
Why?

91
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,130
I'm going to find him right now.

92
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,570
What do you want?

93
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:57,159
Don't you know the rules?

94
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,800
Then I'm not performing.

95
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,820
Suit yourself.

96
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:02,240
So many people want this opportunity.

97
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,840
I don't mind if you withdraw.

98
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:11,920
Ma.

99
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,480
Are you still performing?

100
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:28,320
Of course.

101
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,640
Why wouldn't I?

102
00:07:40,760 --> 00:07:41,600
So,

103
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,290
you've been refusing to go on stage

104
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:47,200
and didn't believe we could win.

105
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,240
About what I said earlier,

106
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,040
I'm sorry.

107
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:54,880
Good luck.

108
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,880
Just don't have any regrets.

109
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,210
Don't you have any regrets?

